{"TopicId":193833,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to lock stages?","CreatedByName":"Lanley Kerman","CreatedById":204349,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-13T09:35:26Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Lanley Kerman","CreatedById":204349,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-13T09:35:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow to lock stages?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-13T09:39:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs in, how to prevent an accidental press of the space bar jettisoning a vital piece of your ship? You could add empty stages between them if you\u2019re doing a long transfer burn or a landing, but it\u2019s not nearly as practical to do that when launching.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Regor","CreatedById":175796,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-13T09:57:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223784560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193833\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589362526\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lanley Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, Lanley Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow to lock stages?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BL\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lanley Kerman","CreatedById":204349,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-17T12:30:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223784569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193833\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589363878\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175796\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mabdi36\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/13/2020 at 5:57 PM, mabdi36 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BL\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhere to put alt\u002Bl tho\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Regor","CreatedById":175796,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-17T13:00:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223786544\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193833\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589718604\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lanley Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n29 minutes ago, Lanley Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhere to put alt\u002Bl tho\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nin flight view. If you don\u0027t want to accidentally stage, press alt\u002BL in flight to lock it, and then alt\u002BL to unlock staging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JcoolTheShipbuilder","CreatedById":204576,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-17T17:19:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand if it doesnt work/gets stuck, you can press alt\u002BF12 and go to input locks and clear the input locks and try again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bestPlayer_xu","CreatedById":204372,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-19T11:28:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe top one of the four buttons at the bottom left (toggle staging, toggle docking mode, toggle map, toggle orbital view) \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}